create file
/etc/ld.so.conf.d/usr-local.conf

with this content
# user lib default configuration
/usr/local/MATLAB/auxlib/

put to that these library files from /usr/local/MATLAB/R2017b/bin/glnxa64:

libmwnetworkdevice.so


run 
sudo ldconfig


- With ldd you can figure out library depndencies

- Joystick configuration
 Mode lamp OFF
 swicth at the back at X (so not D)

